{"tid":2023001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人！五大訴求？係要求，唔好跪得唔得呀。","createTime":"2020-05-18T16:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T17:52:58.000Z","uid":238660,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fde36c477550ea1b290e229cbf958ae846bed176","tid":2023001,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/19/002832_b120fef0e3a68ab970558838dfcf5928.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F19%2F002832_b120fef0e3a68ab970558838dfcf5928.jpeg&h=479651c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足，可唔可以唔好再跪？<br />\n<br />\n唔好向敵人下跪。我地要示威，唔係要示弱呀，由今日開始我唔要見到有任何人跪喺度求赤匪，求暴政呀。<br />\n<br />\n我哋五大訴求個求係要求，唔撚係哀求。 <br />\n<br />\n無論如何你都唔需要跪喺度講野，要講嘅係咁多，明唔明係你嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n呢張圖我已經出過三次，所謂事不過三所以我唔希望我會喺呢個Channel見到第四次。<br />\n<br />\n#唔好撚再跪<br />\n<br />\n香港歷史 <a href=\"https://t.me/Hkhistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHkhistory&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=300d60e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Hkhistory</a>"},{"pid":"255ea00aa1da6609fbd7936e880113305e582b34","tid":2023001,"uid":106666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T16:31:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c6ef01ca38c1e3ebdb5986f4736b3fe11011ca6","tid":2023001,"uid":296244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T16:31:38.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aee1c7130d0878008ff9829f637f132b82a273f","tid":2023001,"uid":328479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c45ba6e4551903f998317ea598a0ab526e796f9","tid":2023001,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep